  "title": "how do i use cWRP with Instantsearch widget?",
  "body": "I have a page which contains links that open the same page again but with a different query, since the component remains the same, react will not unmount and mount back again.\r\n\r\nI want the parameters to change when the same page is opened up with a different query.\r\n\r\nBasically I want to trigger change of state programmatically in my cWRP.\r\n\r\nI am using react-instantsearch beta 18",
